### Test trip modification endpoint
### First, you need to get an access token by logging in

### Login to get access token
POST http://localhost:8000/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=your_email@example.com&password=your_password

### Use the access token from login response to test trip modification
POST http://localhost:8000/trips/modify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "city_name": "Udaipur, Rajasthan, India",
  "place_types": ["museum", "tourist_attraction", "hindu_temple"],
